    "- Log-transformed activity values (Y_log) for stable regression\n",
    "- Train / val / test splits saved to `./data/`\n",
    "- 4 known EGFR inhibitors as validation anchors\n",
    "\n",
    "**Next:** `02_baselines.ipynb` — train all 4 models and measure accuracy + GPU cost."
